title: World Cricket Championship Pro 5.4 (46) Modded Original Unmod ad
description:
Features of this mod:
*Removed all types of ads completely 
*Unlimited batting bowling powerups powerpoints 

What's New
Gangs of Cricket - Form a gang & complete the challenges to earn more points!
Missions - Complete the missions assigned to you & level up!
Shout Board - Chat with others
Share/request points with friends
New set of achievements (Hall Of Fame & Shame) included
Online cloud sync of your points, statistics, Hall of Fame/Shame etc.,
Email validation will give you bonus points!
Stumping results has enhanced
And few minor bug fixes
Note : Some of the features are 2015 Beta release
